metadata.plot: A down-and-out stuntman must find the missing star of his ex-girlfriend's blockbuster film.
metadata.overview: Fresh off an almost career-ending accident, stuntman Colt Seavers has to track down a missing movie star, solve a conspiracy and try to win back the love of his life while still doing his day job.
metadata.title: The Fall Guy

release_dates.note: South by Southwest Film & TV Festival
